metadata.name: Culturedturtle #1397
metadata.description: Culturedturtles is an idea born out of pure love and passion for promoting world peace through art. In a world so complex and filled with a lot of differences, this is our way own little way to promote peace by creating a project that displays the Diverse Cultural outfits of different countries. We aim to educate and bring together people from all over the world to appreciate the Values of each other.
